      "bars": null,
      "chordLines": [],
      "lyricLines": [
        {
          "id": "17353ef4-22a0-48d3-9fb3-7aa1613d86ce",
          "text": "You did me wrong 'cause I let you (Let you)",
          "startTime": 126.854383,
          "endTime": 128.600963
        },
        {
          "id": "eb1a8a66-a4db-43e1-8eb1-8f5252ae3add",
          "text": "Usually, I like my situations beneficial",
          "startTime": 128.600963,
          "endTime": 130.945544
        },
        {
          "id": "a8b2b911-ca2f-45b6-896a-77aae2459243",
          "text": "Doin' somethin' different, got me lookin' stupid (Damn)",
          "startTime": 130.945544,
          "endTime": 133.288129
        },
        {
          "id": "b89d3803-aa7d-43f7-8a07-5da3e52ccd32",
          "text": "The only way I'm comin' back to you is if you dreamin' lucid (Hmm)",
          "startTime": 133.288129,
          "endTime": 136.425181
        },
        {
          "id": "c50405d1-ccf7-46f4-a0db-8ef7ff004062",
          "text": "Prove it, if you made a promise then keep it (Keep it)",
          "startTime": 136.425181,
          "endTime": 138.849353
        },
        {
          "id": "bb62c7db-accb-405f-9ac6-1c7e96003eb1",
          "text": "Why you wanna lie and then get mad I don't believe it (Boy, bye)",
          "startTime": 138.849353,
          "endTime": 141.182823
        },
        {
          "id": "f199596a-a930-4c09-be18-88497f136d53",
          "text": "But really, I was doin' just fine without ya",
          "startTime": 141.182823,
          "endTime": 143.434433
        },
        {
          "id": "e0fbdd77-5123-4511-810a-91bd140ce331",
          "text": "Lookin' fine, sippin' wine, dancin' on club couches (Ah)",
          "startTime": 143.434433,
          "endTime": 146.205476
        },
        {
          "id": "949a7c5f-08ac-45b4-97f4-68e19a8ff45e",
          "text": "Baby, why you wanna lose me like you don't need me? (Don't need me)",
          "startTime": 146.205476,
          "endTime": 148.543503
        },
        {
          "id": "de5d0ced-5e61-4ec0-afc6-dd56ebb87c8d",
          "text": "Like I don't block you and you still try to reach me (Still try to reach me)",
          "startTime": 148.543503,
          "endTime": 150.984501
        },
        {
          "id": "abd1e633-3202-465e-aff9-9e47c2e18d3a",
          "text": "How you figure out how to call me from the TV? (Huh?)",
          "startTime": 150.984501,
          "endTime": 153.276519
        },
        {
          "id": "7f48c809-6ada-47ae-9f98-33cee0234b72",
          "text": "You runnin' outta chances and this time I mean it (Ah)",
          "startTime": 153.276519,
          "endTime": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "64d00f01-4d1b-44ec-8d9f-ab982d5a5b83",
